issue.title: different axis scaling & bin counts
issue.body: Need some more advanced logic to determine how many price bins to use. A logarithmic x-axis would be nice.

issue.title: Shipping ZIP code
issue.body: The shipping ZIP code is hard-coded to 35401. It should be user-specifiable.

issue.title: XML injection possibility
issue.body: Inputs need to be passed through htmlspecialchars($string, ENT_XML1);

issue.title: Encoding
issue.body: What encoding does it use and how badly does it break if you throw emoji or CJK or RTL override at it?
